properties.name: predict.docker-cpu
properties.description: cpu count for pul predicate container.

properties.name: predict.docker-memory
properties.description: memory bytes for pul predicate container.

properties.description: input path for pul predicate, input files will be create under this path.

properties.description: output path for pul predicate, output files will be create under this path.

properties.description: how many days to reserve result.
